metadata.name: Beg For It

Owners of the 'Beg For It' digital collectible receive price advantages for X&ND's future drops, and access to token-gated events, as he rolls out his upcoming album. The 'Beg For It' digital collectible also marks X&ND's first single for the XANDYLANDERS; a day-one community of lovers and broken hearts who have connected with X&ND during live shows, and chose to commemorate their experience through the \"Rise of X&ND\" collection.
